{"tid":623666,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴女車長工會刊憲成立","createTime":"2018-04-10T07:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T11:07:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f6fb3731648e51a048b5f3ca8f4e52ac652a994d","tid":623666,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180410/20357081?_ga=2.74720914.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F20357081%3F_ga%3D2.74720914.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=14dy5Za6T0yLZEhG0Vyge4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=1a5417f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F20357081%3F_ga%3D2.74720914.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=3b8632ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180410/20357081?_ga=2.74720914.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n九巴女車長工會刊憲成立<br />\n<br />\n6.8K<br />\n港聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180410/large/10la6p9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180410%2Flarge%2F10la6p9.jpg&h=b16f7b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n月薪車長大聯盟召集人葉蔚琳獲批成立同名工會。<br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年2月發動九巴車長罷駛的「月薪車長大聯盟」發起人葉蔚琳，獲批成立同名工會。葉蔚琳透露，工會除供九巴車長和運輸業人士申請的「聯繫會員」，亦歡迎公眾申請成為「大聯盟之友」。月薪車長大聯盟獲政府的獨立檢討委員會邀請，稍後提交意見。<br />\n<br />\n月薪車長大聯盟於上月28日獲正式批核，職工會登記局本月6日根據《職工會條例》刊憲。葉蔚琳表示，有關申請在遞交文件後約半個月就已經成功獲批，她形容過程快速和順利。現時月薪車長大聯盟有約200名創會會員，未來會設立「大聯盟之友」的永久會員，亦歡迎公眾申請成為「大聯盟之友」，公眾人士只需要繳交一次入會費和會員費共100元就能入會，但並沒有投票權。九巴車長或運輸業人士則可加入成為「聯繫會員」，入會費和年費各為50元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴士檢委會邀發表意見<br />\n<br />\n葉蔚琳表示，由於工會仍在申請銀行戶口，所以現時僅在準備入會表格，尚未正式招收會員。葉蔚琳指工會會員雖然越多越好，但人數並非是最重要，她個人更着重工會會員有共同的目標和理念。<br />\n<br />\n葉蔚琳又坦言，工會暫時未有財政資源，會址也暫時只作通訊用途。她指「無錢也有無錢」的方法，未來會主力透過網上招收會員和宣傳；工會日前亦獲政府成立的香港巴士專營服務獨立檢討委員會邀請發表意見，她對工會獲肯定感到榮幸，稍後會向委員會提交意見。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅繼盛"},{"pid":"2dea1483ced68b71df9e40d66e1cdceb4b5e5d5f","tid":623666,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"大聯盟之友係咪即係巴膠"},{"pid":"c92d2dfb5999353472fe8d134d85ca72f62c06b8","tid":623666,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/160212_846d66b32aaed8c52e7b76cd5f7b4145.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F160212_846d66b32aaed8c52e7b76cd5f7b4145.png&h=d46a72d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/160213_c1b82fe791eb1a95976ef3ee2d0663cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F160213_c1b82fe791eb1a95976ef3ee2d0663cc.png&h=3d7818c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奶共有得上位<br />\n好撚合理"},{"pid":"ec28195816d563194dc21649a2bb4a41fcee880e","tid":623666,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:38:44.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b3e61904a24da6c5dfd7aaaf1a0cf6908a31e57","tid":623666,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0